// clash.autoDim.json — run-log output of the shared clash-detection + auto-dimension
// pipeline (ClashEngine, AutoDimensionRunner/Engine/Commit, resolvers, pickers), used by
// Clash Finder & Dimension, Clash Finder & Elevation Tag, and Refine Dimensions.
// NOTE: internal tokens (Grid/SlabEdge/ManualDatum, group modes) stay in code; the
// DiagnoseSlabEdge diagnostic lines and the run-grouper/density tuning summaries stay
// hardcoded (developer diagnostics, same policy as DiagnosticsLog).
{
